metadata.name: Within the matrix
metadata.description:
1/1 digital art_  
 3500*3500px 300dpi_  
One day I realized that I was burying my dream in everyday life and social norms. We are taught since childhood to follow the same path. Different storyline, but one scenario for everyone. School->University->Work->Family->End... What if it could be different? I woke up that day.
